  x Dynamic values are not supported in global styles because there is no element to attach them to.
  | Declare a CSS custom property instead and toggle it via an attribute/class on the root element:
  | 
  | globalStyle`:root { --spacing: 4px; } :root[data-compact] { --spacing: 2px; }`
  | 
  | See https://yak.js.org/docs/features#globalstyle
